---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Fees & Funding | Brenkley Doctoral College" description="Transparent fee information for all Brenkley Doctoral College doctoral programmes, including payment plans, funding options, and employer sponsorship guidance.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-b border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">Fees & Funding</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Transparent, Competitive Fees</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">We believe cost should not be a barrier to doctoral study. Our fee structure is transparent, our payment plans are flexible, and we actively support applicants in securing employer sponsorship and external funding.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Programme Fees -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Programme Fees</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">2025/26 Fee Schedule</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">All fees are quoted per year of study unless stated otherwise. Fees are reviewed annually. Students enrolled on a programme are not subject to in-year fee increases.</p>

      <div class="space-y-4">

        <!-- Extended Advanced Diploma -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Extended Advanced Diploma — Year 1 of the PhD</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Main Qualification</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">Eighteen to twenty-four months, delivered fully online. SCQF Level 11, 180 credits, with an applied internship. Equivalent to Year 1 of a PhD — a standalone qualification or foundation for direct progression into PhD Year 2 at a partner university.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">£10,000</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted">Year 1</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border text-sm text-muted">
            Single Year 1 fee of <strong>£10,000</strong>, regardless of whether completed in 18 or 24 months. Instalments available.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Online PhD -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Online PhD</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Doctoral</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">Three to six years. Year 1 is fully online with us; Year 2 onward is with your chosen partner university. For researchers who require maximum schedule flexibility.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">£10,000</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted">Year 1</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border text-sm text-muted">
            Year 1 (Extended Advanced Diploma, delivered fully online) fee shown, instalments available. On completion, you articulate directly into PhD Year 2 at a partner university of your choice — with a UK Student (CAS) visa route available for international researchers — progressing through to PhD graduation, normally at the end of Year 3 for full-time students. Year 2 onward is billed at your chosen partner university's own rate.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Access to Doctorate -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Access to Doctorate</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-training">Pathway</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">One year. A structured foundation pathway for professionals preparing for doctoral-level study.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">£2,800</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted">total</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border text-sm text-muted">
            Single payment or two instalments. Successful completion may lead to exemptions in doctoral entry.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Research Training -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Research Training</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-training">CPD</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">Modular research methods training, available as standalone CPD or integrated within a Brenkley Doctoral College programme.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">£1,500</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted">per module</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border text-sm text-muted">
            Modules include: Research Design, Qualitative Methods, Quantitative Methods, Mixed Methods, Academic Writing, Literature Review.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Supervisor Development -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Supervisor Development</h3>
                <span class="tag tag-training">CPD</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">Professional development for doctoral supervisors. Recognised by Brenkley Doctoral College and acknowledged for CPD portfolios.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">£1,200</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted">total</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border text-sm text-muted">
            Full programme fee. Group rates available for institutional partners. Contact us for organisational pricing.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Payment Plans -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-y border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Flexibility</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Payment Plans</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Annual Payment</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">Pay your annual programme fee in a single payment at the start of each academic year. This is the standard payment route and requires no additional administration.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent">No additional cost</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Semester Instalments</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">Split your annual fee into two equal payments — one at enrolment and one at the midpoint of the academic year. Available to all students on full doctoral programmes.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent">No additional cost</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Monthly Instalments</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-3">Spread the cost of your annual fees across twelve monthly payments via direct debit. A small administration fee applies. Subject to approval and direct debit setup.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent">£95 administration fee per year</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Funding -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Funding Your Doctorate</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Funding Options</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Employer Sponsorship</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">Many Brenkley Doctoral College researchers have their fees fully or partially sponsored by their employer. We provide a standard sponsorship letter template and can meet with HR or Learning & Development teams to explain the value proposition of doctoral-level research for organisations.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Ask about our employer partnership scheme — organisations sponsoring three or more researchers receive a 10% institutional discount and access to our partner briefing events.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Professional Body Bursaries</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">A number of professional bodies offer bursaries or learning grants for members undertaking postgraduate or doctoral study. Eligibility varies by body and membership grade. Brenkley Doctoral College can provide documentation to support applications to professional bursary schemes.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Relevant bodies include the CMI, CIPD, AoC, RICS, and various healthcare professional councils.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Early Enrolment Discount</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">Applicants who enrol and pay their first-year fee in full at least 60 days before their programme start date receive a 5% early enrolment discount on their first year's fees.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">This discount applies once per student and cannot be combined with other promotional discounts.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Career Development Loans</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">Postgraduate and professional development loans may be available through some financial providers for doctoral study costs. Brenkley Doctoral College is able to provide fee confirmation documentation for loan applications.</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">We recommend speaking with your bank or an independent financial adviser about the best loan options for your circumstances.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-t border-border py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Questions about fees?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">Our admissions team is happy to discuss fee options, employer sponsorship, and payment plans. Contact us for a no-obligation conversation.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="/apply" class="btn-primary">Start your application</a>
        <a href="/connect" class="btn-outline">Speak to us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
